        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Readily Ending Debt Under Corporate Engagement Act of 2021 or the REDUCE Act of 2021</strong></p> <p>This bill modifies the tax deduction for interest paid on student loans to allow such deduction without any offset for amounts received as employer-provided educational assistance.</p>]]>
